EU’s Rehn Says ECB Has ‘Very Strong Legitimacy’

-- B y   M e e r a   L o u i s
-- 
2011-09-22T15:08:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-22/eu-s-rehn-says-ecb-has-very-strong-legitimacy-.html
European Union Economic and
Monetary Affairs Commissioner  Olli Rehn  said today that the
 European Central Bank  enjoys “very strong legitimacy.”  “No one is seriously challenging the independence of the
ECB. The ECB enjoys very high legitimacy,” Rehn said at an
event in  Washington .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Meera Louis in Washington at 
